            </div>
            <div class="sector-card">
              <strong>🏅 电力 / 电网</strong>
              <span class="etf-codes">
                <span class="code-pill">POWL</span><span class="code-pill">XLU</span><span class="code-pill">VRT</span><span class="code-pill">NVTS</span><span class="code-pill">POWI</span><span class="code-pill">ON</span><span class="code-pill">WOLF</span><span class="code-pill">AOSL</span><span class="code-pill">XFAB</span><span class="code-pill">000400</span><span class="code-pill">600406</span><span class="code-pill">300750</span><span class="code-pill">600885</span><span class="code-pill">603290</span><span class="code-pill">688187</span><span class="code-pill">600460</span>
              </span>
              <p style="margin:0.5rem 0 0;font-size:0.9rem;color:rgb(var(--gray));"><strong>💹 A股映射：</strong>许继电气（000400）、国电南瑞（600406）、宁德时代（300750）、宏发股份（600885）；功率半导体映射：斯达半导（603290）、时代电气（688187）、士兰微（600460）、三安光电（600703）。<br /><strong>🕒 最近更新：</strong>6/17 Mizuho 称 800V DC 与 CPO 均无延迟，数据中心电力架构升级时间表继续前置。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sector-card">
              <strong>🆕 电子特气 / WF6 / 化合物半导体外延片</strong>
              <span class="etf-codes">
